      out.write("\t\t<ul class=\"text_conversion\">\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t<div class=\"text_conversion_title\">注意事项</div>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t<li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text_conversion_subtitle\">1:镜片佩戴时,请将镜片上两端角度指标以水平方向将镜片付着于角膜。佩戴镜片后，才可以做脸部化妆。卸下镜片后，才可做脸部卸妆。</div>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t<li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text_conversion_subtitle\">2:保持带镜片手指的干燥，若带镜手指指端水分过多。则在带镜时镜片容易与手指粘连若在带镜过程中镜片未能入眼。不要急于再次配戴镜片，而应该将镜片充分冲洗后再带。</div>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t<li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text_conversion_subtitle\">3:佩戴眼镜者要 没有风沙眼 没有眼类疾病。</div>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t<li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text_conversion_subtitle\">4:每天佩戴时间不要超过8小时。</div>\r\n");
